      "content": "Here are a few caption options for your coffee shop's Instagram:\n\n**Option 1 (Focus on Community):** \"At [Shop Name], we believe a truly great community is one where everyone feels welcome. We are committed to fostering an inclusive space for every single person who walks through our doors. Come grab a cup and be part of our diverse community!\"\n\n**Option 2 (Focus on Values):** \"Our commitment to DEI isn't just a buzzword; it's woven into the fabric of our shop. We strive to support diverse voices and create an equitable environment for our staff and customers alike. Taste the difference that genuine inclusion makes!\"\n\n**Option 3 (Short & Punchy):** \"Diversity fuels our passion, and inclusion fuels our coffee! We celebrate the unique backgrounds and perspectives of our community every day. Stop by and see how we're building a more welcoming space, one latte at a time.\"",
