      "content": "those are better for the old school crowd, i get that. but honestly, do you think it's actually bad for a business to avoid these terms? some people say that if a business isn't being explicitly clear about these values, they're basically being complicit in the problems they're ignoring. i'm just trying to figure out if i'm actually doing the right thing by being \"neutral.\"",
